lead_paragraph: Defender Brad Smith's second-half goal rescued a 2-2 draw as injury-hit seven-times FA Cup winners Liverpool denied fourth tier Exeter City a notable third round giantkilling scalp on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Lowly Exeter Hold Second-String Liverpool in FA Cup
headline.main: Lowly Exeter Hold Second-String Liverpool in FA Cup
